originalText.text:
It's my pleasure to recommend Alex Carini and the Carini Group. Alex and his team are extremely responsive, knowledgeable and professional. I travel frequently for business and they made renting and managing my property easy and smooth. Throughout the years, working with Alex not only he did earn my respect and gratitude, but he also distinguishes himself as someone totally worthy of my trust.
I was very impressed with his services as he is:
1. A good listener and therefore knew exactly what his clients wants from the start
2. Flexible as he will go above and beyond to accommodate his client’s needs.
3. Very organized and punctual
4. A very hard worker and rarely gives up

I highly enjoy working with the Carini Group and I will be contacting them again if I’m ever looking to rent, sell or invest again in New York City!
